; Test word-level ops: slice, concat, ite
; 4-bit counter, extract low 2 bits, check if they reach 3
1 sort bitvec 4
2 sort bitvec 2
3 sort bitvec 1
4 zero 1
5 one 1
6 state 1 cnt
7 init 1 6 4
8 add 1 6 5
9 next 1 6 8
; slice low 2 bits
10 slice 2 6 1 0
; bad: low bits == 3
11 constd 2 3
12 eq 3 10 11
13 bad 12
